_:Naa9c7d48708f4270a68410ee9e4d60de <http://schema.org/description> "The Information Commissioner’s Office (ICO) upholds information rights in the public interest, promoting openness by public bodies and data privacy for individuals. ICO is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology ." .
